    function CheckWishList() {

        var SessionLogin = '';
        if (SessionLogin == null || SessionLogin == '') {
            alert('Please log into your account and then add items');
            return false;
        }
        else {
            //var urlpost = "http://localhost:58236/Kyazoonga2014/"
            var urlpost = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://' : 'http://') + "www.kyazoonga.com/";
            urlpost = urlpost + 'WishlistHandler.ashx?s="CreateWish"';
            var xmlRequest = new xmlHttp();
            xmlRequest.url = urlpost;
            xmlRequest.doRequest();
            var rttxt = xmlRequest.xmlRequest.responseText;
            if (rttxt != "0" &amp;&amp; rttxt != "2") {
                Popup.showModal('ctl00_SignInOut_dvWish');
                var table = document.getElementById("WishContent");
                table.innerHTML = rttxt;
            }
            else if (rttxt == "0") {
                alert("There's nothing to see here. Create your wishlist now!");
            }
            else {
                alert("Please Login");
            }
        }

    }

        if (authResult) {

                getFullName();

    function getFullName() {
        // Load the oauth2 libraries to enable the userinfo methods.
        gapi.client.load('plus', 'v1', function () {

            var request = gapi.client.plus.people.get({
                'userId': 'me'
            });
            //            alert(request + '');
            request.execute(getFullNameCallback);

        });
    }
